Say Count installs this reviewed upstream runtime without modifying it. The
editor-side parser, formatter, conversion preview, and installer are separate
Say Count components. The upstream choice-screen customization is not installed
automatically because overwriting a project's screens.rpy would be destructive.
`say_count_chat_bridge.rpy` is a Say Count compatibility file that provides
non-destructive enter/exit labels around the unmodified upstream chat screen.
